result.title: 1996 - 1999 Centre for Environment, Fisheries & Aquaculture Science (Cefas) Sublittoral nematode assemblages from four offshore sites around the UK coast, May 1996 to June 1999
result.name: 1996-1999-centre-for-environment-fisheries-aquaculture-science-cefas-sublittoral-nematode-1999
result.notes:
Data consists of nematode worms and harpacticoid copepod species abundance 
listed as counts per sample. Samples were collected between May 1996 and June 
1999 from four offshore stations around the coast of the UK (Off Tyne, Off 
Humber, Celtic Deep and Lyme Bay).

Data including sediment granulometry and trace metal concentrations is also 
available.
